descriptionHtml:
Powered by CodeXL Solutions, Inc., Aurora is the Philippine’s first Insurance Brokerage
mobile app. Allowing you to conveniently manage all of your insurance policies and
transactions. Aurora will guide you to a better life and help transform the lives of the
people for the better. It makes policy issuance, renewals, and claims easy and simple.

Key App Features:
-Become a Community Influencer
-Purchase Insurance policies
-Monitor Performance
-View Dashboard
-Application Directory
-Initiate Amendments
-Initiate policy claims

descriptionHtml:
Get ready for the future of Protection! Meet our state-of-the-art Aurora App, where you get confidence and convenience in one place, creating an unparalleled insurance experience.

Amazing Protection Products: Find the best policies for you! From essential coverage to specialized choices, our app offers a wide range of options from top-rated providers.

Advocates that Support You: Our app empowers our advocates with the latest tools, so they can assist you faster and better. Expect personalized recommendations that prioritize your needs.

Easy and Simple: Protection has never been easier! Our app simplifies the entire process, allowing you to explore, compare, and secure coverage with just a few taps. No more paperwork or stress!

You're Our Focus: At our core, it's all about you – our valued customer. Our dedicated team is here to support you every step of the way, ensuring peace of mind.

User-Friendly Design: App navigation is a breeze! Our app's easy-to-use interface makes protection accessible to everyone. Get informed and make confident decisions effortlessly.

Your Data is Safe: We prioritize your security. Our app has strict measures in place to protect your information and ensure confidentiality.


Ready to experience a whole new level of Protection? Don't miss out on the fantastic benefits that Aurora offers. Take control of your coverage today – download now and enjoy protection like never before!
